{"type":"message","id":"9828b0ef","parentId":"3e1d50f5","timestamp":"2026-05-25T01:53:53.800Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It looks like the agents list only shows the \"main\" agent. This suggests that the tts agent configuration might have been lost or the gateway restarted in a way that didn't properly reload all agent configurations.\n\nThe situation seems to be:\n1. The cron job \"TK选品每日9AM推送\" was interrupted and appears to be lost (not in the job list)\n2. The tts agent doesn't appear in the agents list - only \"main\" is configured\n3. The gateway restart may have caused configuration loss\n\nThis is concerning. The gateway restart seems to have caused some configuration to be lost. I should inform the user about this and suggest checking the tts agent configuration.\n\nActually, wait - let me think about this more carefully. The cron job notification says \"TK选品每日9AM推送\" failed with \"cron: job interrupted by gateway restart\". This could mean:\n1. The job was running when the gateway restarted, causing the interruption\n2. After restart, the job might still exist but just had a failed run\n\nBut when I list cron jobs, I don't see it. This suggests it was either:\n- Not recreated after restart\n- The restart wiped it\n\nLet me look more carefully. The error says \"job interrupted by gateway restart\" - this is the error message from the cron system when a running job is killed by a restart. The notification was generated to report this failure.\n\nIf the job no longer exists in the list, it could be that:\n1. It was a one-time job that was deleted after running (even failed)\n2. It was a recurring job but the gateway restart caused it to be dropped\n\nGiven the error message \"job interrupted\", it sounds like a running job was killed. But since I can't find it in the list now, either:\n- It was a one-time job that completed (with failure) and was cleaned up\n- Something else happened\n\nActually, looking at the time - the notification is from today (Mon 2026-05-25 09:52 GMT+8). \n\nThe cron expression \"0 9 * * *\" would execute at 9:00 AM, so the job was running when the gateway restarted around that time. I should explain to the user that the configuration appears to have been lost or corrupted during the restart, and recommend they verify whether the tts agent and cron job need to be reconfigured.","thinkingSignature":"ef5f1bcaa47e8c33d4a8b8a97d2d15c28539fec2c762d22ae8955633f446d9ae"},{"type":"text","text":"情况比较清楚了：\n\n**问题分析：**\n1. **Cron 任务丢失**：`TK选品每日9AM推送` 不在当前任务列表中，很可能在 gateway restart 时被丢失\n2. **tts agent 未在列表中显示**：agents_list 只返回了 `main` agent，tts 选品大师的配置也没加载出来\n3. **触发原因**：cron 在 9:00 AM 执行时被 gateway restart 中断\n\n**结论**：Gateway 重启导致 tts 相关的配置（cron 任务 + agent 配置）可能丢失或未正确加载。\n\n🎯 **建议**：\n1. 需要检查 tts 选品大师的配置是否还在\n2. 重新创建每日 9AM 的 cron 推送任务\n\n要不要我帮你检查一下 tts 的配置状态，并重建 cron 任务？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7439,"output":664,"cacheRead":46277,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779674020424,"responseId":"0662dea4cfc1f2db40d43310ad3b614c"}}
